description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maternity Support Worker&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have exciting opportunities for an experienced Maternity Support Worker Band 2 to join the Staff Bank, based at the Queen Alexandra Hospital, Portsmouth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Portsmouth is one of the largest NHS trusts in the country. Joining the Staff Bank as a Maternity Support Worker can offer you a more flexible shift pattern, as well as the opportunities to work across different departments, gaining invaluable skills and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essential Requirements;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 6 months NHS experience in the last three years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to perform and record manual observation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Completed breastfeeding training.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Phlebotomy trained ( desirable not essential )&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DBS checked at level for maternity / children.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;IT skills as many of our services are electronic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank Maternity Support Workers are invaluable to us and in return for their dedication and commitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive pay rates and weekly pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities to work across various departments and sites, gaining invaluable knowledge and experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Priority of shifts over agency workers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An online self-booking system and dedicated bookings team, accommodating your convenience and availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Electronic Timesheet submission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Onsite office and designated Business Partners to offer daily support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A professional AHP Recruitment Team that will ensure you are registered and compliant to work shifts as soon as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated compliance team that will ensure you remain compliant to work, sending out regular expiry updates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We also offer Core Skills Training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please apply directly to this advertisement by submitting your current CV, for further information on the roles please contact the Portsmouth Hospital Staff Bank Team on 0333 577 3316.&lt;/p&gt;
